data.description: What an amazing opportunity to own a charming 2 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath bungalow in the heart of Lakeland.  So many upgrades, yet still the potential to make it your own.  Boasting of high ticket improvements including a newer AC (2021), a newer roof (2019), newer front windows (2020), electrical rewiring throughout (2019), new septic pump and water alarm installed (2023) and more, this home creates high value for any new owner. Both warm and welcoming, it also includes a spacious living area, a beautiful fireplace, laminate flooring, and a large room off of the master bedroom that could be used as an office or large closet. Finally there is an additional room (window and closet) that could be used as a THIRD bedroom.  This home offers many possibilities.  There is so much to love about this home, and it will be the perfect fit for its new owner. Schedule your showing today!
